## Messages API
### GET `/messages`
#### Endpoint
- Method: `GET`
- Full path: `/messages`
- Function: `MessagesController.findAll`

#### Description
Return paginated message logs with optional filtering by message status. Each item’s **`sender`** includes **`isDeleted`** and **`deletedAt`** for the Zalo account that sent the message (so the UI can show when the sender was soft-deleted via `DELETE /zalo-accounts/:id`).

#### Request
- Params: none
- Query:
  - `status`: `MessageStatus`, optional, one of `SENT | FAILED | RECALL`
  - `page`: `number`, optional, default `1`
  - `limit`: `number`, optional, default `20`
- Body: none

Example request:

```json
{
  "status": "SENT",
  "page": 1,
  "limit": 20
}
```

#### Response

```json
{
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "1f0b96fc-c694-4d83-8f4c-20fa20aa0001",
      "messageZaloId": "987654321",
      "cliMsgId": "1713171000000",
      "uidFrom": "1122334455",
      "content": "Hello group",
      "senderId": "7c13f32f-90eb-483f-b5e0-c3b7fa120002",
      "groupId": "5d6a8d48-b45c-43d8-9b0d-5cc3bd110001",
      "sentAt": "2026-04-15T09:00:00.000Z",
      "status": "SENT",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-15T09:00:00.000Z",
      "sender": {
        "id": "7c13f32f-90eb-483f-b5e0-c3b7fa120002",
        "zaloId": "1122334455",
        "name": "Child Account",
        "phone": "0909999999",
        "isDeleted": false,
        "deletedAt": null
      },
      "group": {
        "id": "5d6a8d48-b45c-43d8-9b0d-5cc3bd110001",
        "groupName": "Marketing Team",
        "groupZaloId": "1234567890123456789"
      }
    }
  ],
  "meta": {
    "page": 1,
    "limit": 20,
    "total": 1,
    "totalPages": 1
  }
