#### Response

```json
{
  "id": "3d680e16-4b9a-4ff3-88b0-a0f2ee900001",
  "key": "message_interval",
  "value": "5",
  "updatedAt": "2026-04-15T09:10:00.000Z",
  "minutes": 5
}
```

#### Error cases
